I design H-Bridge circute to control DC motor at 2 direction and can load a current up to 5A.

components:
1-N-channel MOSFET transistor (IRF510)  (4 pieces)
-Max ID: 5.6 A
-VDS : 100v
-Rds=0.54
-Power dissipation: 43 W
-fast switching.
-low price (10 pieces less than 2 $)
Note: The datasheet (https://www.vishay.com/docs/91015/sihf510.pdf)
2-DC mototr ( I use 12v motor but yot can use a bigger)
3-DC voltage source(24 V)
4-pull-up resistor (2 pieces)
5-resistor to prevent latch up (2 pieces)
6-button as switch (2 pieces)
